<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١١١ - <span class="c3">{تَبَّتْ يَدَا أَبِي لَهَبٍ وَتَبَّ}</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">تَبَابٌ:</span> خُسْرَانٌ.<span class="c5"> تَتْبِيبٌ:</span> تَدْمِيرٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(سورة تبَّتْ)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قوله:</span> <span class="c2">(خسران)</span>؛<span class="c5"> أي:</span> كما في قوله تعالى: {وَمَا كَيْدُ فِرْعَوْنَ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>